1
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,500
This is for you.

2
00:00:09,760 --> 00:00:10,760
Happy birthday!

3
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:11,840
Thank you.

4
00:00:13,520 --> 00:00:14,360
When I grow up,

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:16,560
I'll buy you a huge cake.

6
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,440
Really?

7
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:18,780
It's a deal.

8
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,520
Pinky swear.

9
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,240
No changing for a hundred years.

10
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:23,960
Stamp!

11
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,280
Hello.

12
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,920
I'm looking for the presidential suite.

13
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,450
Looking for Sister Xiaoyu?

14
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,690
I'll take you there. This way, please.

15
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,160
Please come in.

16
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,400
Welcome, my good friend,

17
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,640
Bai Qiu.

18
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,120
Xiaoyu.

19
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,520
Here.

20
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,079
Thank you.

21
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,329
You're welcome.

22
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,920
I'll be going now.

23
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,280
Since you're already here,

24
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,210
why don't we have a drink together?

25
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,200
Cheers!

26
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,600
So you're saying,

27
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,880
you resigned?

28
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,560
I went to the TV station

29
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,680
just to make my brother happy.

30
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,400
I didn't like that job at all.

31
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,840
A rich young lady is indeed different.

32
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,640
Others can't even squeeze in,

33
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,240
and you quit just like that.

34
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,160
Stop making fun of me.

35
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,530
Have you ever seen a rich young lady

36
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:29,130
who hasn't figured out next month's rent?

37
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,880
As soon as my brother found out I quit,

38
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,800
he immediately cut off my allowance

39
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,930
and my credit cards.

40
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:36,440
If I don't go work at the coffee shop,

41
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,370
I won't even be able to afford food.

42
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,760
So that's how it is.

43
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,420
It's fine, Bai Qiu.

44
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:48,920
From now on,

45
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,960
if I have a meal,

46
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,420
you'll have a bowl of soup.

47
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,960
Really?

48
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,040
Thank you.

49
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,079
You are so nice.

50
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,360
It's nothing.

51
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,040
Here.

52
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,000
A little gift for you.

53
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,440
Thank you.

54
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,480
From now on, we

55
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,120
are good sisters.

56
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,240
Let's drink.

57
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,280
Start the live stream.

58
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:41,400
Hello, my darlings.

59
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,600
Tonight,

60
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:45,760
any questions about getting beautiful

61
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,800
or making money,

62
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,840
you can ask me all of them.

63
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,440
Thank you very much to all the leaders,

64
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,720
teachers,

65
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,000
media friends,

66
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,480
and all the students present,

67
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,840
as well as Li Weihao's parents.

68
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,330
My name is Chen Rong.

69
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,520
I am a psychologist.

70
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,000
Hello, everyone.

71
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,000
I am Lin Jiaming.

72
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,760
First of all,

73
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:49,920
thank you very much for coming to this conference.

74
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,320
Weihao and I

75
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,159
are childhood friends.

76
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,560
We went to school together

77
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:59,720
and spent a happy childhood together.

78
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,680
His departure

79
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,560
was a huge blow to me.

80
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,820
I'm reflecting on myself.

81
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,680
I'm reflecting on whether I was there for him

82
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,240
when he needed help

83
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,040
and support the most.

84
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,440
At the same time, I'm reflecting on whether

85
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,960
I have truly paid attention to

86
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,400
the mental health of every student.

87
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,280
Therefore,

88
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,640
Lin Group has decided

89
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,280
to fund and establish

90
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,720
the Qiongzhou University

91
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:32,000
Campus Mental Health Foundation.

92
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,720
This is not only for Qiongzhou University

93
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:37,159
but also for thousands of students,

94
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,440
and more importantly,

95
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,840
for thousands of Li Weihaos.

96
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:44,000
To commemorate Li Weihao,

97
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,560
our undergraduate teaching building

98
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:48,090
will be officially renamed Weihao Building.

99
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,440
Let us remember the pain,

100
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,880
never forget,

101
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,880
and look forward.

102
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:57,840
Well,

103
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,960
before the start of this conference,

104
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,920
I would like to invite

105
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,320
Li Weihao's parents to the stage.

106
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,040
Please.

107
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,280
I would like

108
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,160
to give you two a hug.

109
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,730
It's been hard on you

110
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,000
these days.

111
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,760
Pretentious.

112
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,480
Next,

113
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,560
let's invite

114
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,960
Mr. Lin Yongtai, Director of Lin Group,

115
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:53,720
and Du Xuefeng, President of Qiongzhou University,

116
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,720
to present the consolation money

117
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,050
to Li Weihao's parents.

118
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,160
High-sounding.

119
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,880
Lastly,

120
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:37,080
let's take out the green ribbons,

121
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,920
and together, let's contribute

122
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:43,160
to campus mental health.

123
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:57,040
Weihao, we love you.

124
00:09:57,040 --> 00:10:10,880
Happy birthday!

125
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:15,040
Happy birthday to our birthday boy, Li Weihao!

126
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,200
No.

127
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,680
What is this?

128
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,530
Consolation money.

129
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,740
What are you doing?

130
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,640
Don't just stand there.

131
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,240
Turn it off.

132
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,400
Turn it off.

133
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,640
What is this?

134
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,520
This is not real.

135
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,720
This is not me.

136
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:34,520
Turn it off.

137
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,400
How do I turn this off?

138
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:39,360
Weihao.

139
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:01,000
Son!

140
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,480
How could this happen?

141
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,600
Guixiang.

142
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,720
Guixiang.

143
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:12,520
Quick, call an ambulance!

144
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,280
Cut off the power.

145
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,160
Are you okay?

146
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,240
Weihao's mother. Guixiang.

147
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,400
Murderer.

148
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,240
Murderer.

149
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:29,040
Murderer.

150
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,200
None of it is true.

151
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,720
Can you handle it?

152
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,690
Come on, keep drinking.

153
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:48,800
Come on.

154
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:05,160
Murderer.

155
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:06,760
Zhang Chao.

156
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,840
Zhang Chao.

157
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,540
Stand right there.

158
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,840
Stop right there.

159
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,800
Let me ask you,

160
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,240
did you touch my phone?

161
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,160
Next time you delete photos,

162
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,840
remember to delete the backup too.

163
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,160
You are so shameless.

164
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,960
I wasn't the one hitting people.

165
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,560
You are the shameless ones.

166
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,800
I'm not done with you.

167
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,080
What are you doing, Ah Fu?

168
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,680
Look at the time,

169
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:34,880
and you're still fighting here.

170
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,160
Isn't today chaotic enough?

171
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,200
Ms. Chen,

172
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,330
you're just in time.

173
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,760
This guy

174
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:42,160
keeps saying he has nothing to do with Li Weihao,

175
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,320
that they are not friends,

176
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,640
but behind our backs, he stands up for him over and over again.

177
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,370
He is the one who did this today.

178
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,400
Also,

179
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,960
he was the one who drew graffiti on the wall last time.

180
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,080
At the bar, wearing a mask,

181
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,680
he was the one who beat up my boss.

182
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:56,120
And he was the one pretending to be a ghost in the middle of the night.

183
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,280
Zhang Chao, if you have the guts today,

184
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,160
explain it clearly in front of Ms. Chen.

185
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,600
Did you do it or not?

186
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,800
I did it.

187
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,320
I did it, so what can you do to me?

188
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,080
Ms. Chen, he admitted it.

189
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,560
He admitted that he did it.

190
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:09,640
It wasn't me.

191
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,100
You're pretending again.

192
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,320
What are you pretending for?

193
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,560
You just admitted it.

194
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:14,680
Say it again.

195
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,520
Was it you, Zhang Chao?

196
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,440
Say something, Ah Fu.

197
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:16,920
Tell me.

198
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:18,320
It wasn't me.

199
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,780
Ms. Chen, he's a total psycho.

200
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,160
A big idiot.

201
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:35,050
One minute he admits it, the next he denies it.

202
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,680
Don't hit my son.

203
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:23,000
Please don't come in.

204
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,640
Stop bothering us, please.

205
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,440
I beg you.

206
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:27,680
Don't hit my son. My son is dead.

207
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,320
You said he had depression,

208
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,080
and I believed it.

209
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,120
But now what?

210
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:34,200
A school bullying incident came out.

211
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:38,160
Is this the explanation your school is giving me?

212
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:40,160
Rest assured,

213
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:40,880
regarding this matter,

214
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,440
we will thoroughly investigate it to the end

215
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,120
and punish those responsible without leniency.

216
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,960
Save it.

217
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,960
Weihao's dad,

218
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,040
please calm down.

219
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:49,160
The principal brought us here just to check on you

220
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,440
and tell you to take care of yourselves.

221
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,560
I will never believe you again.

222
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,640
We also came today hoping you know

223
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,480
that the school stands with you.

224
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,120
Whenever you need help,

225
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,360
you can come to us anytime.

226
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,720
Who is with you?

227
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,560
You are all in this together.

228
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:05,200
Don't bother us anymore.

229
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,080
It's okay.

230
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:23,680
How could this happen?

231
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:27,920
It's okay.

232
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:30,320
How could this happen?

233
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,960
Chao! Chao!

234
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,480
Chao, come look!

235
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,400
The surveillance video of the graffiti guy from that night

236
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,520
has been uploaded.

237
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:55,480
But this video is so blurry.

238
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,240
And this person is wearing a mask.

239
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,770
We probably can't find him.

240
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:00,370
What should we do, Chao?

241
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:02,480
This is...

242
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:06,080
It's too blurry.

243
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,960
Wait, this mask is so weird.

244
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,040
Who could it be?

245
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,850
Can the image quality be restored?

246
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:13,120
Chao,

247
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:15,120
can you handle this?

248
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:53,090
He's the one who did this today.

249
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,040
Also,

250
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:56,640
he's the one who drew graffiti on the wall last time.

251
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:57,760
He's the one who wore a mask in the bar

252
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:59,360
and hit my boss.

253
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:03,000
He's also the one who pretended to be a ghost in the middle of the night to scare people.

254
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:03,800
Impossible.

255
00:17:05,319 --> 00:17:06,119
No way.

256
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:09,579
Why is this happening?

257
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:30,680
Ah Fu, where are you?

258
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:32,560
Why aren't you answering?

259
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:35,490
Do you have anything to tell me about the foundation?

260
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,120
What is there to say?

261
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,520
How would I dare to speak?

262
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:06,600
Why are you drinking in broad daylight?

263
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:08,360
Damn it.

264
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:10,360
You are sneaking around in broad daylight.

265
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:12,200
Trying to scare your old man to death?

266
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:15,280
No, why did you come back?

267
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:17,340
I missed you, so I came back to see you.

268
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,040
Oh, right.

269
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,560
I'm not at the age where I'm dying.

270
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:23,290
So why do you need to come see me?

271
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,600
Go back to school.

272
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,320
Where am I supposed to go, Dad?

273
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,880
I have no classes today.

274
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,540
No classes?

275
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:37,560
Did you do something bad at school?

276
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,600
Did you?

277
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:41,160
What bad thing could I do?

278
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:42,320
You're drunk.

279
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:43,480
Look at you.

280
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,840
Hurry, go. Really?

281
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:45,760
Really, I didn't.

282
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:46,760
I'm telling you, go inside.

283
00:21:46,760 --> 00:21:47,960
Take your studies seriously.

284
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,000
I told you not to drink so much.

285
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,530
And you're still drinking.

286
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,440
Can't you turn off your phone? It's so noisy.

287
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,560
Hang up.

288
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,360
Hello?

289
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:58,520
Why are you calling?

290
00:21:58,520 --> 00:21:59,120
Why are you calling?

291
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:01,680
All you do is call all day. It's so noisy.

