464
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,360
Survival,

465
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:52,680
love,

466
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:54,400
interpersonal relationships.

467
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:56,320
None of these are simple issues.

468
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,360
Many people don't even realize

469
